    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function's complexity is low as it performs a straightforward operation of converting a numeric input to a string and padding it with zeros. It involves basic string manipulation and does not include complex logic or multiple steps."
